xo  number questions  questionsnumber The cmavo 
   xo, a member of selma'o PA, is used to ask questions whose answers are numbers. Like most Lojban question words, it fills the blank where the answer should go. (See 

    for more on Lojban questions.)

te'u  JOhI selma'o  jo'i  vector indicatorterminator for  vectorcomponents of  jo'iprecedence of  vector indicator 
   jo'i, the only cmavo of selma'o JOhI, is the vector indicator: it has a syntax reminiscent of a forethought operator, but has very high precedence. The components must be simple operands rather than full expressions (unless parenthesized). A vector can have any number of components; 

